The '''Arjan II logic computer''' was a [[Droid brain/Legends|droid brain]] that was a designed to rival [[SyntheTech/Legends|SyntheTech's]] [[AA-1 VerboBrain/Legends|AA-1 VerboBrain]]. The [[Computer/Legends|computer]] was found primarily as the central processor of the [[Roche Hive Mechanical Apparatus Design and Construction Activity for Those Who Need the Hive's Machines/Legends|Roche Hive Mechanical Apparatus Design and Construction Activity for Those Who Need the Hive's Machines]] [[J9 worker drone/Legends|J9 worker drone]].<ref name="EGTD">''[[The Essential Guide to Droids]]''</ref>

